      The BCP-47 language tag of this locale. Android resolves it to whichever values-* folder it
      picks for the app's strings, so it always matches the language the UI is displayed in. The app
      reports it to the backend (via the Accept-Language header) so account emails are localised to
      the same language. It is not user-facing; provide one value per values-* folder so every
      supported locale reports its own tag.
    -->
